Title: Maleficent: Mistress of Evil
Writer: Linda Woolverton, Noah Harpster, Micah Fitzerman-Blue, Charles Perrault (based on: characters from "La Belle Au Bois Dormant" written by), Bek Smith
Actors: Angelina Jolie, Elle Fanning, Harris Dickinson, Michelle Pfeiffer
Plot: Maleficent and her goddaughter Aurora begin to question the complex family ties that bind them as they are pulled in different directions by impending nuptials, unexpected allies and dark new forces at play.
Awards: Nominated for 1 Oscar. Another 1 win & 10 nominations.
